{"questionId":"1247719","questionHtml":"<p>Calculate the ratio <span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\"><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\frac{{{V_C}}}{{{V_B}}}\">\n  <mfrac>\n    <mrow>\n      <mrow>\n        <msub>\n          <mi>V</mi>\n          <mi>C</mi>\n        </msub>\n      </mrow>\n    </mrow>\n    <mrow>\n      <mrow>\n        <msub>\n          <mi>V</mi>\n          <mi>B</mi>\n        </msub>\n      </mrow>\n    </mrow>\n  </mfrac>\n</math></span> </span>where <em>V<sub>C</sub></em> is the volume of the gas at C and <em>V<sub>B</sub></em> is the volume at B.</p>","markschemeHtml":"<p><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\"><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"{T_B}V_B^{\\frac{2}{3}} = {T_C}V_C^{\\frac{2}{3}} \\Rightarrow \\frac{{{V_C}}}{{{V_B}}} = {\\left( {\\frac{{{T_B}}}{{{T_C}}}} \\right)^{\\frac{3}{2}}}\">\n  <mrow>\n    <msub>\n      <mi>T</mi>\n      <mi>B</mi>\n    </msub>\n  </mrow>\n  <msubsup>\n    <mi>V</mi>\n    <mi>B</mi>\n    <mrow>\n      <mfrac>\n        <mn>2</mn>\n        <mn>3</mn>\n      </mfrac>\n    </mrow>\n  </msubsup>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mrow>\n    <msub>\n      <mi>T</mi>\n      <mi>C</mi>\n    </msub>\n  </mrow>\n  <msubsup>\n    <mi>V</mi>\n    <mi>C</mi>\n    <mrow>\n      <mfrac>\n        <mn>2</mn>\n        <mn>3</mn>\n      </mfrac>\n    </mrow>\n  </msubsup>\n  <mo stretchy=\"false\">⇒</mo>\n  <mfrac>\n    <mrow>\n      <mrow>\n        <msub>\n          <mi>V</mi>\n          <mi>C</mi>\n        </msub>\n      </mrow>\n    </mrow>\n    <mrow>\n      <mrow>\n        <msub>\n          <mi>V</mi>\n          <mi>B</mi>\n        </msub>\n      </mrow>\n    </mrow>\n  </mfrac>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mrow>\n    <msup>\n      <mrow>\n        <mo>(</mo>\n        <mrow>\n          <mfrac>\n            <mrow>\n              <mrow>\n                <msub>\n                  <mi>T</mi>\n                  <mi>B</mi>\n                </msub>\n              </mrow>\n            </mrow>\n            <mrow>\n              <mrow>\n                <msub>\n                  <mi>T</mi>\n                  <mi>C</mi>\n                </msub>\n              </mrow>\n            </mrow>\n          </mfrac>\n        </mrow>\n        <mo>)</mo>\n      </mrow>\n      <mrow>\n        <mfrac>\n          <mn>3</mn>\n          <mn>2</mn>\n        </mfrac>\n      </mrow>\n    </msup>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span>&nbsp;</span> ✔</p>\n<p><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\"><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\frac{{{V_C}}}{{{V_B}}} = {\\left( {\\frac{{620}}{{340}}} \\right)^{\\frac{3}{2}}} = 2.5\">\n  <mfrac>\n    <mrow>\n      <mrow>\n        <msub>\n          <mi>V</mi>\n          <mi>C</mi>\n        </msub>\n      </mrow>\n    </mrow>\n    <mrow>\n      <mrow>\n        <msub>\n          <mi>V</mi>\n          <mi>B</mi>\n        </msub>\n      </mrow>\n    </mrow>\n  </mfrac>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mrow>\n    <msup>\n      <mrow>\n        <mo>(</mo>\n        <mrow>\n          <mfrac>\n            <mrow>\n              <mn>620</mn>\n            </mrow>\n            <mrow>\n              <mn>340</mn>\n            </mrow>\n          </mfrac>\n        </mrow>\n        <mo>)</mo>\n      </mrow>\n      <mrow>\n        <mfrac>\n          <mn>3</mn>\n          <mn>2</mn>\n        </mfrac>\n      </mrow>\n    </msup>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mn>2.5</mn>\n</math></span></span> ✔</p>\n<p><em>Award <strong>[2]</strong> for bald correct answer.</em></p>","meta":{"questionId":"1247719","referenceCode":"19M.2.HL.TZ1.7b.iii","subjectId":"59-dp-physics-first-assessment-2025","title":"Calculate the ratio V C V B where VC is the volume of the gas at C and VB is the volume at B.","paper":"2","level":"HL","questionNumber":"b.iii","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 2]","breadcrumbLabels":["B. The particulate nature of matter","B.4 Thermodynamics"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}},"schema